Package civitas.celestis.math.vector

Class Vector3

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.math.vector.Vector3
All Implemented Interfaces:
DoubleVector<Vector3>, Vector<Double,Vector3>, Collectable<Double>, Listable<Double>, Groupable<Double>, Transformable<Double>, Serializable
public class Vector3 extends Object implements DoubleVector<Vector3>
A three-dimensional double vector which uses XYZ notation.
